---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About — Trion Holdings" description="Family-owned diversified investment firm since 1977, Trion Holdings builds and scales businesses across real estate, hospitality, and more with hands-on operational expertise.">
  <main>




    <!-- Top Banner -->
        <section class="relative flex min-h-[50vh] md:min-h-[70vh] w-full items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-bottom" style="background-image: url('/banner-bg-3.jpg');">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1A1919]/80 via-[#1A1919]/65 to-[#1A1919]"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl px-4 mb-20 mt-52 text-center text-white">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
                    About Us
                </h1>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg sm:text-xl">
                    "From tacos to tech to timeless properties, Trion Holdings partners with businesses that are ready to scale and make an impact."
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Section Separator -->
        <div style="background: #f3f3f3;">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1440 193"><path fill="#e3ba63" d="m0 74.286 987.143 46.19L980 169.048 0 186.667z"/><path fill="#1a1919" d="M0 0h1440v64.286l-221.43 128.571L0 76.191z"/></svg>
        </div>




    <!-- 2 Column Section -->
    <section class="bg-[#1A19190D] px-4 py-16 md:py-32 color-copy z-0" style="z-index: -1;">
        <div class="max-width mx-auto flex flex-row flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap gap-12 items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                <div class="w-32 mt-30 md:mt-0 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-white">
                    
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4 mt-8 md:mt-14">
                    Family Owned &amp; Operated Since 1977
                </h1>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#E3BA63] mb-6"></div>
                <p class="leading-6 mb-4">
                    For more than 45 years, Trion Holdings has grown from a family-owned real estate platform into a diversified investment company with holdings across hospitality, real estate, and other growth industries. We bring together the strength of institutional discipline with the creativity and agility of a family enterprise.
                </p>
                <p class="leading-6 mb-4">
                    Our approach is grounded in conservative underwriting, operational expertise, and hands-on management. By leveraging a trusted network of industry partners, we identify opportunities where scaling, repositioning, and strategic execution can unlock significant value.
                </p>
                <p class="leading-6">
                    Whether building for sustained growth or positioning for a strategic exit, Trion Holdings invests with purpose—driving performance while preserving the entrepreneurial spirit that has defined us since 1977.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-1/2 md:h-full block">
                <img src="/trion-holdings-family-owned.webp" alt="Trion's Family Photo" class="w-full h-auto object-cover z-0" decoding="async" width="840" height="556" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- Section Separator -->
    <div class="w-full bg-white overflow-hidden">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="presentation" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1512 78" class="w-full aspect-[1512/78] mb-2"><path fill="#f3f3f3" d="M0 0h1512L0 78V0Z"/></svg>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Leadership section -->
    <section class="px-4 py-20 leadership-spacing">
        <div class="max-width mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl">Leadership</h2>
                <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[color:var(--trion-gold-2)] mt-4 mx-auto"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
                <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-center" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgb(255 255 255 / 0), rgb(255 255 255));">
                    <img src="/carmelo-milio-trion-headshot-v2.webp" alt="Carmelo Milio, CEO Trion Holdings" class="w-[84%] max-w-[84%] object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="744" height="816" />
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-6 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold headline-font-family">Carmelo Milio, CEO</h3>
                        <p class="text-[color:var(--trion-gold)] mt-1 text-base">Chief Executive Officer</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 text-base">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-xl">Professional Experience</h4>
                        <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">Trion Holdings LLC, CEO &amp; Founder</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2015 - Present</p>
                        <p class="leading-5 mt-2">Founded Trion Holdings as a platform for acquiring diversified investments and value-add real estate properties in New York City and the Tri-State.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-xl">Past Partnerships and/or Acquisitions</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-4 text-base">
                            <li>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">Multifamily Property: Greenwich, Connecticut</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2025 - Real Estate</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">Airbnb: Single Family Home Investment</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2022 - Real Estate</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">Commercial Real Estate Acquisition</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2021 - Real Estate</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">Silver Sands Motel and Restaurant</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2021 - Hospitality/Real Estate</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">The Taco Project</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2018 - Hospitality/QSR</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4">Gipper, Inc. and CredReady, Inc.</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-0">2016 - Technology Start-Ups</p>
                            </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                            <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3 text-xl">Education</h4>
                            <div>
                                <p class="font-semibold mb-0 leading-4 text-base">Pace University Lubin School of Business</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-5">BA in Business Administration</p>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">1998-2002</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

              <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-xl">Community &amp; Memberships</h4>
                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-base">
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[color:var(--trion-gold)] text-lg">✓</span>
                    <p><a href="https://thebcw.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Business Council of Westchester</a></p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[color:var(--trion-gold)] text-lg">✓</span>
                    <p>Member of the National Association of REALTORS</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[color:var(--trion-gold)] text-lg">✓</span>
                    <p>Past President and Trustee of the Building &amp; Realtors Institute (BRI)</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[color:var(--trion-gold)] text-lg">✓</span>
                    <p>Certified Property Manager (CPM<sup>&reg;</sup>)</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-[color:var(--trion-gold)] text-lg">✓</span>
                    <p>Member of exclusive business and leadership communities centered on scaling, innovation, and legacy building</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
